commit.message:
Prevent schematron-related SXWN9000 Saxon error

Fixes https://github.com/relaxng/jing-trang/issues/240
See https://github.com/relaxng/jing-trang/issues/240#issuecomment-446897726
add openjdk early access but allow it to fail

Use source=7, target=1.7 for target Java version

Without this change the build otherwise emits the following warnings:

```
[javac] warning: [options] source value 6 is obsolete and will be removed in a future release
[javac] warning: [options] target value 1.6 is obsolete and will be removed in a future release
```

https://github.com/relaxng/jing-trang/pull/243#issuecomment-446396499
also seems to indicate that in Java 12, source=6/target=1.6 will
apparently become an error case rather than a warning case.

Thanks @innovimax

commit.message:
Automate publishing to Central Repo and GitHub

This change adds a Python script and Ant build files for automating
publication of Maven jing and trang artifacts to the Central Repo —
along with adding a new lib/maven-ant-tasks-2.1.3.jar file which is a
dependency that Ant needs to do the actual packaging/publishing steps.

The Python script added in this change also fully automates publishing
of GitHub releases of the zipped jing.jar and trang.jar distributions.

The change also includes adjustments to eliminate errors and warnings
that would otherwise be generated during the javadoc build.

Fixes https://github.com/relaxng/jing-trang/issues/98
Supersedes https://github.com/relaxng/jing-trang/pull/203
Add .gitignore

commit.message:
Moved docs to the relaxng.org repository (#238)

* Moved docs to the relaxng.org repository

* Make build populate docs dir from submodule

This change adds https://github.com/relaxng/relaxng.org as a submodule
and updates the (ant) build to make it populate the `docs` subdirectory
by copying over files from the (new) relaxng.org submodule.

The build needs the `docs` content in order to create the jing and trang
zip release distributions with the docs included.

* Moved docs to the relaxng.org repository

This change adds https://github.com/relaxng/relaxng.org as a submodule
and updates the (ant) build to make it populate the `docs` subdirectory
by copying over files from the (new) relaxng.org submodule.

The build needs the `docs` content in order to create the jing and trang
zip release distributions with the docs included.
